messages.speech:
Prices of Recyclables:

Car battery is around ₱100 per kilo.
Electronic scrap/defective computer parts ranges from ₱8.00 to ₱300.00 per kilo.
Glass bottles ranges from ₱0.25 to ₱2.00 per kilo.
Metals ranges from ₱3.00 to ₱300.00 per kilo.
Paper scraps ranges from ₱1.50 to ₱8.00 per kilo.
Plastics ranges from ₱5.00 to ₱50.00 per kilo.
